ing local routing online</span></button><button data-operator-action=\"sync-live\" type=\"button\" class=\"operator-action\"><strong>Sync Providers</strong><span>Import current live configuration</span></button><button data-operator-action=\"refresh-setup\" type=\"button\" class=\"operator-action\"><strong>Check Setup</strong><span>Validate auth, tools, MCP, and config</span></button><button data-operator-action=\"stream-check\" type=\"button\" class=\"operator-action\"><strong>Check Streams</strong><span>Probe selected framework providers</span></button><button data-operator-action=\"write-suite\" type=\"button\" class=\"operator-action\"><strong>Write Suite Status</strong><span>Publish Moon suite discovery state</span></button></div></section><section class=\"connection-board\" id=\"connection-board\"><div class=\"connection-head\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Connect</p><h2>Client Endpoints</h2></div><span id=\"connection-copy-status\">Copy full URLs</span></div><div class=\"connection-grid\"><article class=\"connection-card\"><div><strong>OpenAI Chat</strong><small>OpenAI-compatible clients</small></div><code data-url-path=\"/v1/chat/completions\">/v1/chat/completions</code><button data-copy-path=\"/v1/chat/completions\" type=\"button\" class=\"button-secondary\">Copy</button></article><article class=\"connection-card\"><div><strong>OpenAI Responses</strong><small>Codex-style responses clients</small></div><code data-url-path=\"/v1/responses\">/v1/responses</code><button data-copy-path=\"/v1/responses\" type=\"button\" class=\"button-secondary\">Copy</button></article><article class=\"connection-card\"><div><strong>Anthropic Messages</strong><small>Claude-compatible clients</small></div><code data-url-path=\"/v1/messages\">/v1/messages</code><button data-copy-path=\"/v1/messages\" type=\"button\" class=\"button-secondary\">Copy</button></article><article class=\"connection-card\"><div><strong>Claude Desktop</strong><small>Desktop gateway route</small></div><code da