ort MCP Apps</button></div></div><div class=\"setup-grid\"><div class=\"setup-card\"><div class=\"setup-card-head\"><strong>Auth</strong><span class=\"state warn\" id=\"setup-auth-state\">Loading</span></div><div class=\"setup-list\" id=\"setup-auth-rows\"></div></div><div class=\"setup-card\"><div class=\"setup-card-head\"><strong>Runtime</strong><span class=\"state warn\" id=\"setup-runtime-state\">Loading</span></div><div class=\"setup-list\" id=\"setup-runtime-rows\"></div></div><div class=\"setup-card\"><div class=\"setup-card-head\"><strong>Claude Desktop</strong><span class=\"state warn\" id=\"setup-desktop-state\">Loading</span></div><div class=\"setup-list\" id=\"setup-desktop-rows\"></div><div class=\"inline-actions\"><button type=\"button\" id=\"setup-import-claude-desktop\">Import Claude Desktop</button></div></div><div class=\"setup-card\"><div class=\"setup-card-head\"><strong>MCP and Plugin</strong><span class=\"state warn\" id=\"setup-mcp-state\">Loading</span></div><div class=\"setup-list\" id=\"setup-mcp-rows\"></div></div></div><div class=\"table-wrap setup-table-wrap\"><table><thead><tr><th>Framework</th><th>Config</th><th>Proxy Takeover</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead><tbody id=\"setup-config-rows\"></tbody></table></div></article><article class=\"panel wide\" id=\"suite\"><div class=\"panel-head\"><div><p class=\"eyebrow\">Suite</p><h2>Moon Suite Integration</h2></div><div class=\"inline-actions\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"button-secondary\" id=\"suite-refresh\">Refresh Suite</button><button type=\"button\" id=\"suite-write-status\">Write Status</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"button-secondary\" id=\"suite-write-moonclaw\">Write MoonClaw</button></div></div><div class=\"usage-metrics\"><div><span>Status</span><strong id=\"suite-status-state\">-</strong></div><div><span>Apps</span><strong id=\"suite-app-count\">-</strong></div><div><span>Capabilities</span><strong id=\"suite-capability-count\">-</strong></div><div><span>Status File